Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:44.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102332,104083}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106419,107378}Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108546,110548}What are you doing, Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110548,112342}There's going to be a contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112342,113718}A contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113718,115970}You know Miki from our class?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:56.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115970,116721}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:00.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116721,120808}She's entering the Junior Design Contest\Nthat the city's putting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120808,124020}And I'm going to\Nmodel the wedding dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:06.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124562,126439}Model? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126439,129317}She said I'm perfect for it.\NI've already gone for the fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129317,132945}I'm just waiting to see\Nthe finished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132945,134989}And who's going to be the groom?\NThe Frog Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.70,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:135907,138701}{\an2\fad(200,200)}Frog's Bride
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139160,140870}How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:24.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140870,144874}Asuka Jr., you're always\Nmaking fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144874,148920}It's nothing, I'm just being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:30.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149170,150088}Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153966,155259}Miss Takamiya…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:41.26,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:157970,161265}Contest in Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180326,183162}Is there something you want from me,\NMiss Takamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:06.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183162,186290}Oh, nothing.\NI just happen to be going this way, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186290,188209}Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188209,189377}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203975,206310}Darn. She got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213985,215737}Hush, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216446,218239}You must be quiet in the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:41.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218740,221117}I finally got away from Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:44.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221117,224746}She's been following me all over\Nthe for place the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:48.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224746,228374}Really?\NShe's very persistent, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228374,230960}By the way, have you seen Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232003,235423}My wedding dress\Nis supposed to be ready today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:04:00.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236048,240386}She… came to see me about that,\Njust a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241387,242847}She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243347,245391}Yes. The truth is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247977,249937}What did you want\Nto talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:14.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250772,254025}Someone stole the\Ndrawing for my design.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254025,255777}Who'd do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256402,257236}I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265453,268748}Oh, I'm so sorry.\NI have such long legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269415,270875}Miss Suzushiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272418,275922}It's Suzushiro from Group E.\NWe're competing in the same contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275922,277757}Mami Suzushiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:42.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279091,282804}Yes.\NI'm sure that's when it was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283221,286307}She's always thought\Nof me as a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:53.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288935,293439}If she uses my design in the contest,\Nit'll put me in a difficult position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:59.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294482,299654}Because her presentation\Ncomes before mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301197,303991}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303991,305660}Miki, don't lose faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:10.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306661,310456}The right will always be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313876,315586}And that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:20.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315586,320550}I see… and I was\Nlooking forward to the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:25.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320967,325012}Meimi, please get\Nher design back for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325888,328641}Alright! Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328641,330852}At least, I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330852,332645}It's Miss Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332645,336607}With her following me around,\NI can't turn into St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336607,339443}Don't give up hope.\NYou'll think of something, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339777,342363}I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:46.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342363,346409}I want to wear that wedding dress\Nand model in the contest too! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346951,349871}I understand.\NI'll help you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350705,351873}You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:55.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352373,355585}I'll fix you an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355585,358838}In the meantime,\Nyou become St. Tail and get the design.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359338,361841}Hold on.\NWhat do you mean by alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:08.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362383,368264}First, you specify the contest's date\Non the challenge to Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368264,369015}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:09.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369015,369807}And then…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:15.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371434,375271}"…at the Conversational\NEnglish Seminar…"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375688,377773}Hey, Asuka, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377773,379483}Be quiet, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379942,383487}I asked you if you wanted to know\NSt. Tail's identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384071,385323}Are you still harping on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:29.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385323,389076}What a pest.\NI told you what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:32.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389076,392455}I don't care who she is!\NI just want to arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394040,395917}All right then, I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395917,398044}Fine, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399712,401881}Junior Design Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:46.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402590,406677}So this is what Haneoka's\Nbeen worked up about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406677,408638}What's so great about it, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411891,415144}"Tomorrow, at the\NJunior Design Contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:07:00.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415144,420900}I will steal Mami Suzushiro's wedding\Ndress design drawing. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421442,422860}Of all the nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423611,424695}I've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424695,425738}I knew she'd make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425738,428991}That St. Tail…\Nshe's after a wedding dress this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428991,432411}I'm going to follow my own lead\Nthis time. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432411,433371}Huh, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433704,436540}We'll soon learn\NSt. Tail's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439293,440670}Suit yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452640,455810}You were so cute back then, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:39.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455810,459230}And you were a bit slimmer, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:44.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460272,464235}No magic will bring\Nback the old you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464235,465236}Of all the…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465903,467947}Change back,\Nchange back, change back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467947,470157}Or something like that… wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476998,479000}Oh, it's you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479000,480835}Shame on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480835,483504}You're a professional magician.\NThat shouldn't catch you off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483504,486048}Well, I… what's up, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:11.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487842,491637}There's a wedding\Ndress contest tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491637,494015}I'm one of the models.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499061,503899}She's going to get married\None of these days, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:27.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503899,507653}It's too early to start\Ngetting lonely, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:36.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512825,516120}Tomorrow, I have to\Nbe St. Tail and a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517079,519415}I've got to work hard at both!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522710,523586}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525713,527590}You want to go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:52.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528799,532053}I'm sorry, Ruby,\Nyou have to stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:11.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547860,551947}Hey you,\Nyou better do a good job protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551947,554617}Sure, of course, to some degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554617,556368}What do you mean,\N"to some degree"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:23.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556368,563000}I mean, St. Tail is sure to appear\Nafter the contest begins. That's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563000,564293}You're positive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564293,567671}Yes, that's why you\Ncan relax until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567671,568964}So, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571467,573385}I think they can protect themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.38,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:573385,575387}Green Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584188,586357}What are you doing here,\NMiss Takamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586357,587608}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:52.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587608,592279}I was looking for a phone.\NI have to call Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592279,593364}You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593364,594115}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594949,596826}You're not wearing an ID tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:10:00.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596826,600287}Only models and contestants are\Nallowed in here. Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605292,607753}She's sticking to you like glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607753,610256}She's not moving from that spot,\Nnot for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:15.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612049,615803}Seira, are you sure it's all right\Nfor me to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615803,618264}You have nothing\Nto worry about, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618264,620349}Right, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620349,622434}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622935,624436}You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624436,626814}Is that Mami Suzushiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:27.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626814,627731}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630234,632027}That dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632027,634196}It's definitely the one I designed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635781,637658}I won't let them get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:43.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640452,643122}Let's put on a good show,\Nshall we, Kono?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643497,645124}Yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645583,647001}See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:55.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649753,655551}{\i1}The city's Junior Design Contest\Nwill soon begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655551,657845}{\i1}Final preparations are being made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:01.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657845,661473}{\i1}All contestants,\Nplease assemble on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662099,663601}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663601,665769}I'll be there as soon as I change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665769,669148}Don't worry, I'll help her change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669148,670983}Thank you. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675487,677781}Takamiya, you're welcome to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677781,678908}Oh, gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:29.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685122,689043}Seira, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:29.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689043,689960}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694965,696550}She's changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699220,700512}We've got to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:46.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703182,706477}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711565,712483}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714818,716153}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:00.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718072,720115}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734421,736298}Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:20.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736298,740302}Transforming into\NSt. Tail quietly is so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740302,741512}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747643,750145}Oh Seira, you're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:34.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750145,754817}Once I put on the wig and veil,\Neveryone will think it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754817,757611}Oh dear, and\NI'm supposed to be a nun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:42.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757611,762157}I'm counting on you to put on\Na good act and keep Takamiya here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:44.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762157,764868}I will, be careful too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:50.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767162,770833}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774670,776797}What are those two doing in there?
Comment: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:56.79,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:776797,776797}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:02.80,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:782803,782803}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:07.80,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:787808,787808}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790769,791770}Miss…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:15.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792813,795649}Judging by your looks\Nyou must be one of the models.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796817,799236}The contest is starting.\NYou'd better change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799570,801238}But, I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:22.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801697,802948}Is this your dressing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802948,804616}N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:26.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804616,806201}Then it's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806201,807328}W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807911,809830}You're making a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810581,812499}Meimi, now's your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812499,813042}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:42.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819590,822843}I thought I saw\Na black shadow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822843,824970}It must have been your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828015,829058}Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829058,830309}Show's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830642,832144}I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832144,833020}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840444,842363}{\i1}Everything is going good so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842363,843906}{\i1}Now for the hard part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846116,848786}{\i1}We will begin the judging shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850329,852748}{\i1}Entry #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858545,859380}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860214,861131}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861131,862383}My design!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864301,867137}Look! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871183,873519}When is she going to\Nturn into St. Tail, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875270,877314}{\i1}Hurry up, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878857,880526}Haneoka, don't you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881026,883195}Yes, but my number is last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883904,884822}Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891203,893664}{\i1}Oh, Meimi, please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:14:59.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898961,899878}Whoah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906468,907886}Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913100,914351}Please, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:24.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919731,924945}{\i1}We are experiencing a power failure.\NFor your safety, please remain seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:28.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924945,928031}St. Tail is here in the hall!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928615,931952}That's impossible!\NHaneoka's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934872,935956}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:39.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935956,939585}The entire hall is in an uproar,\Nbut stand by, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939585,940627}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944506,945924}Takamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948093,949511}Phew. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952139,955476}Now, I've got to get this ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955809,958312}{\i1}Everyone, quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958312,960898}What's going on there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962524,963567}That's the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:10.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966778,970073}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974745,977039}Hey! Wait! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978707,981293}Sorry, you have\Nto wear that instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981293,982878}I'm taking the design.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986465,989510}I'm giving this back\Nto the real designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989510,990385}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990385,992679}Don't just stand there, get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992679,995682}Just hold it! What does she mean,\N"real designer"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995682,996683}Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:39.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996683,999436}And this is in apology\Nfor causing such a commotion here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007444,1008612}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009196,1010155}Bouquets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015160,1017329}For the future brides.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:00.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019831,1020791}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:01.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020791,1021667}Bouquets from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021667,1022459}I want one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022459,1023544}Ooh, they're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:05.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024211,1025462}Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026171,1028590}Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031134,1032886}She got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035639,1037349}And what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037349,1038600}None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.43,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1038600,1041436}{\an2\fad(0,500)}Junior Designer Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042396,1044022}There, it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044648,1046233}Fly up high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058287,1059329}Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059329,1060831}She's heading for the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069298,1070632}She got away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071842,1073260}Where's Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074928,1075679}Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076221,1077639}Now where's she going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.89,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1077639,1078890}Green Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081393,1083437}I-Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085814,1088191}What'd you come back here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:24.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100329,1104374}Well, Asuka Jr., isn't she beautiful?\NFor goodness sake, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104374,1106168}Miki, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107169,1109630}Yeah, really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113342,1115260}Really very beautiful…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115844,1117512}Your design that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117512,1119723}Oh my, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:43.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120057,1123143}But that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123143,1126938}So… So that's what St. Tail was after!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:51.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126938,1131151}He's trying to change the subject.\NHow typical of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134029,1135530}Asuka, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:56.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136073,1136990}O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:19:01.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136990,1141745}{\i1}Entry #30, you're up next.\NReport to the stage immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141745,1143038}Meimi, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:03.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143038,1143830}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:15.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152130,1155175}Hey, Takamiya,\Nyou can go without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155175,1156927}Asuka, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157469,1159012}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:19.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159012,1159888}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:26.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163141,1166687}And the winning entry in\Nthe Junior Designers Contest is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168105,1171525}#30, Miki Kono's design!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:35.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174111,1175404}Miki, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175404,1176697}Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176697,1177864}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177864,1179449}It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:48.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185122,1188333}{\i1}A wedding dress sure is mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188333,1190335}{\i1}It even makes\NHaneoka seem different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:53.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190877,1193714}And what if she's St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194256,1195006}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195632,1198760}I'm asking you how you'd feel\Nif she was St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:03.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200345,1203724}What are you talking about?\NThat's a really bad joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204099,1206309}It's no joke.\NI'll even make a bet on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:10.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206727,1210439}Stop it! Is that why\Nyou've been following her around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210439,1212190}She's one of your classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212733,1215152}All right, how about this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:20.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215152,1220991}If Meimi Haneoka isn't St. Tail,\Nthen I'll stop following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220991,1222075}You promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:26.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222492,1226663}But if I'm right,\Nyou'll have to date me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226663,1227414}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228999,1230208}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230208,1232961}You promise\Nyou'll stop following her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235255,1236423}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239968,1241845}{\i1}There's no way…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:45.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242262,1245307}{\i1}Haneoka is St. Tail.
