Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:06.99,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1261615,1266995}before we shared our first kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:14.00,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1267454,1274002}for the reason I was crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:19.96,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1275045,1279966}I don't know what I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:28.47,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1280467,1288475}It's the first time in my life\NI feel like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:38.10,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1288809,1298109}Ah, you still don't know so many things,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:44.99,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1298401,1304991}Ah, even though you know me pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:51.99,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1304991,1311998}Hey, my biggest silent wish
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:58.83,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1311998,1318839}is for you to not end up hating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:04.76,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1319214,1324761}I'd be devastated if you did.
